snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedApi

client = AsyncSeedApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.submit_form_data(
        username="johndoe",
        email="john@example.com",
    )


asyncio.run(main())
